in the case of wagtail where category is injected

```
class Category(OscarWagtailAbstractCategory):
    def get_absolute_url(self):
        return self.get_url()

    def serve(self, request, *args, **kwargs):
        cls = get_class('catalogue.views', 'ProductCategoryView')

        kwargs.update({'page': self.page_ptr})

        response = cls.as_view()(request, category=self, **kwargs)

        return response
```

this is a little more optimal

